        <li><i class="fa fa-check-double"></i> <b>Connecting</b> students with leaders in the computing field</li>
        <li><i class="fa fa-check-double"></i> <b>Encouraging</b> the pursuit of career opportunities in computing</li>
        <li><i class="fa fa-check-double"></i> <b>Mentoring and tutoring</b> students for academic and professional success</li>
        <li><i class="fa fa-check-double"></i> <b>Broadening</b> both the University and local K-12 STEM communities through ACM</li>
        <li><i class="fa fa-check-double"></i> <b>Building</b> a network of students, to include current, former, and future; businesses; and local leaders for the benefit of ACM members</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
